WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.858 --> 00:00:05.434
What more doyou want
from us? Why can'tyou
just let us go?

00:00:05.496 --> 00:00:08.302
[ Rainbird ]
You can'tjust be let go.

00:00:08.367 --> 00:00:11.372
l don't think your father
even believes that now.

00:00:11.436 --> 00:00:15.645
- You're dangerous,
and you know it.
- That's not my fault!

00:00:15.708 --> 00:00:19.716
l know that.
l don't care about that.
All l care about is you.

00:00:19.780 --> 00:00:23.889
Now come up here!
Don't make me shoot your father.

00:00:23.951 --> 00:00:27.992
- Don't listen to him, Charlie.
- Promise he'll be all right?

00:00:28.055 --> 00:00:32.330
- l giveyou my real word.
- [Andy] Don't do it, baby.

00:00:32.394 --> 00:00:34.866
- Areyou sure?
- Yes.

00:00:40.637 --> 00:00:42.640
[ Whinnying ]

00:00:45.476 --> 00:00:47.646
Kill him.

00:01:07.902 --> 00:01:10.641
-Jump.
- [ Groaning ]

00:01:10.705 --> 00:01:14.045
No!

00:01:14.109 --> 00:01:16.848
[ Groaning ]

00:01:16.912 --> 00:01:19.550
No! Oh, Daddy!

00:01:19.615 --> 00:01:21.786
Oh, no.
Charlie.

00:01:21.852 --> 00:01:25.826
[ Sobbing ]
Daddy, Daddy,
you're bleeding.

00:01:25.889 --> 00:01:30.064
- Charlie.
- Daddy.

00:01:30.127 --> 00:01:33.400
Look at me.

00:01:37.068 --> 00:01:39.741
[ Rainbird ]
Charlie, look at me.

00:01:42.809 --> 00:01:46.049
That's it.
So l can seeyour eyes.

00:01:49.817 --> 00:01:51.987
l loveyou, Charlie.

00:02:02.999 --> 00:02:06.239
l loveyou!
[ Screaming ]

00:02:06.302 --> 00:02:08.508
[ Continues Screaming ]

